","tid":1188431,"uid":165336,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"126b6ecf5a1b1fecf120714297d7c2bd3ae15032","tid":1188431,"uid":144529,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"小李直頭係比作者棄左，其實當年我以為係三主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鳴門-忍術  佐助-瞳術  小李-體術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"以前興李小龍咪整個功夫佬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家唔興啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪唔玩佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1433af5b4f82ec838c1c985b6e44b15afa23a1","tid":1188431,"uid":43309,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:25:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】<br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：維園草地<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合、3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地遊行至金鐘添美道立法會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/SNRN6c7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNRN6c7.gif&h=5f0c0e94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08239a497a5d4889ed6b45d7cc817cdac303d612","tid":1188431,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"岸本比左個朵比小李叫努力的天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06e802e14ab95978c5939790ef05d1508082ed2","tid":1188431,"uid":43785,"like":18,"dislike":18,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"545f13869096be5c8c44bf487bf66c150abbc56e","tid":1188431,"uid":43785,"like":18,"dislike":17,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一，<br />\n好心你唔識就收皮啦。帶土，佐助果D同佢有天資，但心術不正一樣走錯路。<br />\n<br />\n人柱力史上可以做到咁，更係小之有小<br />\n好心睇下我愛羅，琳同其他人，都係好悲慘既結局。<br />\n<br />\n你冇咁既資質，冇咁既奇遇，都學唔到九陽神功。<br />\n童年時生活更悲慘， 其實好多小朋友已經走上絕路， 好心你哋班毒撚唔好睇嘢睇到咁簡單。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"主角變到咁勁嘅當然係由作者塑造好多奇遇畀佢。<br />\n我的英雄學院咪又係好在識得人輸內功。<br />\n海賊王咪又係有個好老豆好老師好兄弟同紅髮送個果實畀佢食。<br />\n一拳超人咪又係要日日做鍛鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超合金黑光都係日日鍛鍊都冇主角奇遇。<br />\n全職獵人咪又係有老豆有老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要盲目批評火影忍者，火影忍者世界第一<br />\n火影排喺世界第一係不爭嘅事實。<br />\n大結局一個星期，一千個相關post洗動漫台<br />\n全香港市民大大小小大部分都知道乜嘢係火影忍者， 新一代年青人更係睇火影忍者大。<br />\n<br />\n火影忍者喺香港人心目中絕對係第一位<br />\n火影忍者喺歐美各洲 已經超越咗佢地本土漫畫， 你見好多不論黑人白人鬼仔鬼佬全部都識得火影忍者。<br />\n<br />\n你可以扮智者唔欣賞火影，但係其他人個個人都欣賞，會唔會係你自己嘅問題。<br />\n而且我亦都發覺你對火影了解根本就唔深，<br />\n不如你重睇一次火影了解咗人哋講乜嘢先啦"},{"pid":"57f5d3900c03028e4cef5458d4f7e4eac5407cec","tid":1188431,"uid":31389,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"成套野就係:求撚其啦"},{"pid":"37e7cdd295013feec90cfd709b9dda3c356d54a4","tid":1188431,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57f5d3900c03028e4cef5458d4f7e4eac5407cec","tid":1188431,"uid":31389,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"成套野就係:求撚其啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e878773415da72a7981887d838f3cbaf78d5d4","tid":1188431,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"269acebd623cae17e150c1ffd89448afbf917497","tid":1188431,"uid":165336,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"126b6ecf5a1b1fecf120714297d7c2bd3ae15032","tid":1188431,"uid":144529,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"小李直頭係比作者棄左，其實當年我以為係三主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鳴門-忍術  佐助-瞳術  小李-體術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"以前興李小龍咪整個功夫佬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><